User-Registration-Login-System
This project is a full-stack web application that provides User Registration, Login, and Admin Management functionality using Vue.js on the frontend and Spring Boot on the backend. It follows RESTful architecture, layered backend design, and secure authentication practices.

Frontend
-Vue.js 3
-Vite
-Axios
-Vue Router
-HTML, CSS, JavaScript
Backend
-Java
-Spring Boot
-Spring Security
-Spring Data JPA (Hibernate)
DataBase
-MYSQL
Tools
-Maven
-Git & GitHub
-Postman

Vue.js UI
|
Axios (HTTP Requests)
|
Spring Boot REST API
|
Spring Security + CORS
|
Service Layer
|
Repository (JPA)
|
MySQL Database
